China International Marine Said to Offer Guarantee on Loan

-- B y   W e n d y   M o c k
-- 
2011-11-28T07:15:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-11-28/china-international-marine-said-to-offer-guarantee-on-loan.html
China International Marine
Containers Group Co. (200039)  is offering a parent guarantee for a $300
million loan being borrowed by its Hong Kong unit, according to
a person familiar with the matter.  The Shenzhen-based designer of containers and airport
facilities hired HSBC holdings Plc, ING Groep NV and Standard
Chartered Plc to arrange the facility, another person said on
Nov. 10. The loan is being marketed to other lenders in general
syndication.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Wendy Mock in Hong Kong at 
 wmock3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shelley Smith at 
 ssmith118@bloomberg.net  